{"tid":1793004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星火大狀：法律開支向612報銷","createTime":"2019-12-22T05:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T22:59:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3115085aff7081798504c0c3b426967b06260021","tid":1793004,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:06:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191222/4FS7US3H4GCIPU7JHLHUWL5OEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191222%2F4FS7US3H4GCIPU7JHLHUWL5OEA%2F&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=da6e49e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191222%2F4FS7US3H4GCIPU7JHLHUWL5OEA%2F&h=4780491a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191222/4FS7US3H4GCIPU7JHLHUWL5OEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n星火大狀：法律開支向612報銷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191222/large/1576945222_759a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191222%2Flarge%2F1576945222_759a.png&h=2d7b5204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火同盟<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】支援抗爭的星火同盟（星火）日前被警方指控洗黑錢，籌得的7,000多萬元款項被凍結，不少港人對被捕者的法律支援會否因而受阻感到擔心。有協助示威運動被捕者的義務大律師稱，星火的支出一直只用於援助被捕者生活，法律開支由612人道支援基金負責，被捕者獲得的法律支援不會減少。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：習上台後「電視認罪」大增<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n款項作被捕者生活費<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟義務大律師麥雅媛接受傳媒訪問解釋，星火本身扮演一個平台，讓律師接觸被捕人士以提供法律服務，法律援助費用一直由612人道支援基金處理，星火籌得的款項主要涵蓋被捕者飲食和交通等日常生活開支。有熟悉被捕支援服務的人士指出，包括星火等多個被捕支援熱線的運作模式都類同，熱線接獲求助後就會轉介給律師團隊，律師跟進完就會自行向612基金報銷。<br />\n<br />\n根據612基金的工作簡報，截至11月30日，基金籌得超過9,700萬元，總支出接近2,400萬元，有6,946人次接受過服務。當中近400萬元用於法律援助。而最大筆支出則用於「緊急經濟支援/撫恤金」，達910萬元。<br />\n<br />\n義務律師蔡梓慧表示，示威者被捕後所需的即時法律支援牽涉的費用很少，上庭後才會有顯著支出。同時，大部份義務律師並非為錢，被捕者所得到的法律支援不會減少。<br />\n<br />\n■記者關冠麒"},{"pid":"808a85b8fcb926a5f90625ee1beff0bf24aca690","tid":1793004,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">聲援維吾爾族人權集會</span><br />\n12.22 星期日 <br />\n時間 : 15:30<br />\n地點 : 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對通知書</span><br />\n學生歷量<br />\n公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Pk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FPk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=7d4a2b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Pk5KnVQ-VmmyPPOe8ltrJw</a>"},{"pid":"1b80294a70a0da5c11f0b597a144417e40b2bce1","tid":1793004,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvWvjyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvWvjyz.jpg&h=40cdd777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日三點半，麻煩大家準時！<br />\n現場唔好有連豬，連狗<br />\n尊重返人哋啲宗教<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqzgZyw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqzgZyw.gif&h=07bb1026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，&Ouml;zil畀人屌到屎眼爛都冇跪<br />\n我哋聽日都要支持佢<br />\n<br />\nStand with Uyghur(We ga）, Stand with &Ouml;zil（奧燒）"},{"pid":"1aa7d4cddac36b7ab51154173803ee9fcb1772cb","tid":1793004,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T22:59:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZdaEHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZdaEHQ&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=8ad88bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZdaEHQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TeCa7iS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTeCa7iS.png&h=72b9e76e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9RNqWcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9RNqWcd.jpg&h=b591eada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SiUpYy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SiUpYy&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=11be4bcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2SiUpYy</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTCB2Se.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTCB2Se.png&h=18b9bce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRetweet啦<br />\n聽晚出嚟同國際講<br />\n今日凍結得星火7000萬<br />\n令手足支援受阻<br />\n聽日可以凍結你戶口！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41E1uU6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41E1uU6.jpg&h=17080ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"}]}